{"word":"Ἀδώνιος","slug":"Ἀδώνιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n1539\" key=\"*)adw/nios\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ἀδών-ιος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, rare form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἄδωνις</foreign>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.756c</biblScope></bibl>. <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n1539.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ος</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of Adonis</tr_>:—hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀδώνιον, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen></foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a statue of him</tr_> borne in the Adonia, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n1539.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> (sub. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μέτρον</foreign>) a kind of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">verse</tr_>, consisting of a dactyl and spondee, Sacerd.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg9010.tlg001:p.516\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.516</biblScope> </bibl> K. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n1539.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">Ἄδωνις</ref> </xr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg9010.tlg001:111\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">111</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0978.phi001:21:60\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"a